title: Google Nexus 6P to go on sale in India in November
text:
Google Nexus 6P to go on sale in India in November 
Times Of India Saturday 24th October, 2015 
Huawei, which manufactures and sells Nexus 6P, will sell the top Google smartphone in batches because of unprecedented demand for the handset. The company will start delivering units in the Indian market starting the first week of November....
